{"tid":2489247,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB《開心大綜藝》惡搞特首林鄭　通訊局收250宗投訴","createTime":"2021-04-14T23:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T23:21:08.000Z","uid":271829,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ee2025c4384a5e877482f7ef3a8cb2b1e75ae7a5","tid":2489247,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T23:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uNRSYtVPUUP-81qA7dxC2fww5N8=/535x300/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OKGTBIOAFJBR5NMWQHWKNULZLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuNRSYtVPUUP-81qA7dxC2fww5N8%3D%2F535x300%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOKGTBIOAFJBR5NMWQHWKNULZLA.jpg&h=4e83f649&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sWE65tPD46OU9eiOVbUNzLCQJyE=/535x271/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DVOZGT2AANFQZHH2DHGVW62UHI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsWE65tPD46OU9eiOVbUNzLCQJyE%3D%2F535x271%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDVOZGT2AANFQZHH2DHGVW62UHI.JPG&h=bd35ab08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上次惡搞姜濤出事，今次照樣擺姜濤上枱。（電視截圖）<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n冒牌特首堅稱不封關<br />\n阮兆祥指一名姓曾的男子確診患上「矮仔症」，指疫情已擴散，其他主持則扮演記者質問藍太，冒牌特首王祖藍擺出閃縮眼神稱不會封關，之後阿Bob走出來搗亂大叫︰「食屎」，陸永指打兩支疫苗加埋有120%防疫，之後又播出王祖藍同李亞男的照片，指二人是「垂正結婚」，畫面又播出姜濤照片，指歡迎他來TVB。玩完一輪後，扮記者的森美指有「五大缺失」，而王祖藍表明會尋回做節目的初心，介紹多個新節目後，畫面打出「以上內容純屬同大家開個玩笑，觀眾唔好太認真啊」字句。<br />\n<br />\n王喜：侮辱公職人員、危害國家安全<br />\n事後有網民批TVB舊橋當新招，沿用十多年前《獎門人》的環節、甚至遠到半世紀以前的《歡樂今宵》的橋段，以大堆頭胡鬧笑料、無聊當有趣的遊戲充斥整個節目。亦有人以港台《頭條新聞》王喜在「驚方訊息」環節中，扮演「忠勇毅」警察，事後被通訊局警告指內容涉辱警做例子，最後港台宣佈暫停製作節目，後會無期。對於今次輪到無綫玩出火，收到250宗投訴，王喜以短訊回覆《蘋果》投訴TVB：「侮辱公職人員，分裂人民團結、情節嚴重惡劣、危害國家安全。」網民亦指今次TVB有侮辱特首之嫌，應該予以停播作懲罰。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210415/NKUL7LTX7BCWTLLYOMOR36OBBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210415%2FNKUL7LTX7BCWTLLYOMOR36OBBE%2F&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sL%2FjevXO%2BySp3REELKrGah4%3D&h=ad129529\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210415%2FNKUL7LTX7BCWTLLYOMOR36OBBE%2F&h=1624b56f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210415/NKUL7LTX7BCWTLLYOMOR36OBBE/</a>"},{"pid":"82827852f94dc0b92c8c817592156aaede586276","tid":2489247,"uid":37525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T23:16:13.000Z","msg":"推到腰斬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467f7b02b242f0d0ca302915e6ecf08912a4550d","tid":2489247,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T23:20:24.000Z","msg":"全民做投訴師"},{"pid":"b7b76cb74ffd998233c2cb4bd50875a4ffe730d4","tid":2489247,"uid":42526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T23:21:08.000Z","msg":"直情報國安"}]}